WEBVTT

01:38.360 --> 01:40.640
EPISODE 24

01:42.080 --> 01:44.560
How did the video in my phone vanish?

01:44.640 --> 01:47.360
Did you delete it by accident?

01:47.440 --> 01:51.040
I don't think so.
Did you push the wrong button?

01:55.480 --> 01:59.240
Erxi, I always thought
you were a good girl.

02:00.920 --> 02:02.360
A very good friend.

02:02.440 --> 02:04.080
Who wants to be your friend?

02:09.600 --> 02:11.480
What are those two doing together?

03:11.800 --> 03:14.080
Take a look at this resume.

03:26.440 --> 03:29.640
Organize this material.
Get it done before noon.

03:30.400 --> 03:32.840
Erxi, type up three copies
of the files in the drive.

03:32.920 --> 03:35.000
Bind them and file them away.

03:35.080 --> 03:36.320
And this, too.

03:36.400 --> 03:38.360
Get these reviewed by all divisions
and bring them back for me to sign.

03:44.200 --> 03:46.280
Zhao Erxi, Mr. Zhen wants to see you.

03:47.040 --> 03:49.120
He's waiting. Go now.

03:57.520 --> 03:59.160
What's going on?

03:59.440 --> 04:00.760
Counterattack?

04:14.040 --> 04:14.880
Come in.

04:19.959 --> 04:21.000
Mr. Zhen.

04:21.680 --> 04:22.800
Shut the door.

04:28.280 --> 04:29.520
I have a few questions for you.

04:29.600 --> 04:31.360
Don't be nervous. Just sit.

04:36.320 --> 04:37.160
Sit down.

04:41.200 --> 04:43.040
You're not Luwei Weiwei, are you?

04:47.600 --> 04:48.440
No.

04:52.320 --> 04:54.360
Why did you say so during the interview?

04:55.480 --> 05:00.600
Because the interviewers asked
if I ever play games.

05:01.000 --> 05:02.680
I didn't at the time,

05:02.920 --> 05:06.640
so I borrowed my roommate's handle.

05:13.520 --> 05:16.480
Did I get hired, because I said
I was Luwei Weiwei?

05:17.840 --> 05:18.680
You could say that.

05:22.400 --> 05:24.640
So, you're her roommate?

05:28.000 --> 05:29.600
She doesn't go to BIT?

05:29.840 --> 05:33.560
Your roommate goes to Qing University?
What's her name?

05:33.960 --> 05:36.960
Mr. Zhen, if it's not about work,

05:37.040 --> 05:38.240
I should get going.

05:39.840 --> 05:40.680
Don't go!

05:44.160 --> 05:47.360
She goes to QU,
yet she lied and said she went to BIT.

05:48.000 --> 05:51.280
Why do Qing University girls
all have such attitude?

05:58.760 --> 06:01.960
Well, I'm free now. I'll do this myself.

06:02.240 --> 06:05.080
Um... I'll type this up myself.

06:07.200 --> 06:09.600
I'll organize the material.

06:15.400 --> 06:19.160
You're so pathetic, Zhao Erxi.

06:20.280 --> 06:22.480
Everything you have,

06:23.040 --> 06:27.240
including the in-game spouse
and an easy job,

06:27.920 --> 06:30.000
all came about because of Bei Weiwei.

06:36.840 --> 06:39.160
ZHIYI TECH

06:48.480 --> 06:51.160
These are my recommendations and ideas

06:51.240 --> 06:52.480
on the new home system.

06:54.560 --> 06:58.840
Take your time to review them.
I want to head back early today.

07:00.240 --> 07:01.440
Be careful on the road.

07:30.000 --> 07:31.400
What's the meaning of this?

07:33.640 --> 07:34.960
I'm moving back to campus.

07:35.040 --> 07:38.440
There's an empty bed in the dorm
of a graduate student I know.

07:38.520 --> 07:40.680
Don't be impulsive. Let's talk!

07:41.120 --> 07:43.760
Why did you tell Cao Guang
I'm Huantian Xidi?

07:43.840 --> 07:45.600
You think I haven't been
embarrassed enough?

07:46.400 --> 07:50.680
No, Cao Guang mistakenly thought
I was two-timing him.

07:50.760 --> 07:52.240
I only found out what happened,

07:52.320 --> 07:53.840
when I confronted him.

07:54.680 --> 07:58.240
I never told him you were Huantian Xidi.

07:59.160 --> 08:02.280
He must have guessed it, himself.

08:03.360 --> 08:05.160
Sorry, I accused you wrongly.

08:05.600 --> 08:07.360
I should know, you're not like that.

08:08.840 --> 08:11.280
Are we cool now?

08:14.040 --> 08:19.480
Weiwei, compared to me,
you're prettier, smarter,

08:19.840 --> 08:21.560
and more likable.

08:22.880 --> 08:24.680
I've always known this.

08:25.640 --> 08:28.320
I never wanted to fight you for anything.

08:29.440 --> 08:31.080
But why must everything I have

08:32.200 --> 08:35.360
come my way only because of you?

08:36.000 --> 08:39.480
My job, the nice treatment I enjoy,

08:40.200 --> 08:41.919
the person I like,

08:42.600 --> 08:46.160
all fell in my lap,
only because I was mistaken for you.

08:47.440 --> 08:51.600
If you were me, Weiwei,
what would you do?

08:54.680 --> 08:56.160
I don't blame you,

08:57.240 --> 09:00.080
but I simply don't know
how to face you anymore.

09:10.240 --> 09:12.840
This is the money I owe you. Here you go.

09:13.440 --> 09:15.120
I'm moving back to campus.

09:16.760 --> 09:20.400
You said, you don't blame me.
Aren't you blaming me now?

09:22.280 --> 09:26.160
You said, everything happened
because of me.

09:28.400 --> 09:33.920
Fine. Don't leave. I'll go.

09:48.040 --> 09:51.080
This cake is for you,
as a token of my sincere apologies.

09:51.160 --> 09:52.520
Your Highness, please accept it.

09:57.840 --> 10:00.040
It's your favorite cake.

10:01.080 --> 10:01.920
Get out!

10:49.320 --> 10:54.720
Weiwei, compared to me,
you're prettier, smarter,

10:55.080 --> 10:56.800
and more likable.

10:58.120 --> 11:00.520
I've always known this.

11:00.880 --> 11:03.560
I never wanted to fight you for anything.

11:04.760 --> 11:06.600
But why must everything I have

11:07.440 --> 11:10.360
come my way only because of you?

11:11.240 --> 11:14.680
My job, the nice treatment I enjoy,

11:15.480 --> 11:17.160
the person I like,

11:17.800 --> 11:21.840
all fell in my lap,
only because I was mistaken for you.

11:22.680 --> 11:26.840
If you were me, Weiwei,
what would you do?

11:29.920 --> 11:31.480
I don't blame you,

11:32.520 --> 11:35.360
but I simply don't know
how to face you anymore.

12:14.760 --> 12:17.640
Do you still have work to do?

12:18.280 --> 12:21.240
Would I be bothering you,
coming here so late?

12:23.200 --> 12:26.960
Don't act so gingerly around me.
I'm not used to it.

12:31.480 --> 12:34.720
Then get back to your work.
I want to be alone for a while.

12:36.760 --> 12:37.600
Okay.

14:20.960 --> 14:21.800
What are you working on?

14:23.640 --> 14:26.120
A tool that automatically decreases
less important textures

14:26.840 --> 14:30.720
and simplifies models,
based on human visual characteristics.

14:38.840 --> 14:39.680
You feel better now?

14:45.920 --> 14:48.080
Erxi doesn't want to live with me.

14:49.320 --> 14:50.920
So I moved out.

14:55.120 --> 14:59.520
I said, if anyone's leaving, it's me.

15:01.080 --> 15:04.520
Smart girl. You know where to go.

15:06.320 --> 15:08.720
Come on, let's eat something.

15:09.400 --> 15:10.480
Xiao Nai...

15:19.440 --> 15:20.640
Will we fight, in the future?

15:22.360 --> 15:23.200
No.

15:26.320 --> 15:27.160
Why not?

15:29.960 --> 15:34.000
Because we can solve all of our problems
without fighting.

15:38.000 --> 15:43.640
You'll never get mad, no matter what I do?

15:47.320 --> 15:48.360
I won't get mad.

15:52.560 --> 15:56.400
Will we always be happy?

15:59.080 --> 15:59.920
Yes.

16:04.040 --> 16:08.200
But, I used to think,

16:09.120 --> 16:12.960
Erxi and I would always be happy, too.

16:20.160 --> 16:25.640
Weiwei, she's only
a small part of your life.

16:26.680 --> 16:28.320
I'm your everything.

16:40.800 --> 16:42.400
Don't cry for someone else again.

16:44.880 --> 16:46.280
I've never made you cry.

16:50.800 --> 16:52.320
Says who?

16:54.600 --> 16:58.520
I cried, when you didn't show up
at the finals.

17:04.119 --> 17:05.160
You were very upset?

17:08.079 --> 17:08.920
Yes.

17:25.040 --> 17:27.040
I haven't had dinner yet.

17:29.480 --> 17:30.800
Come give me a hand.

18:15.640 --> 18:18.520
I think I'll have to borrow money again.

18:19.080 --> 18:21.600
I don't have enough to stay at a hotel.

18:23.320 --> 18:24.160
You should stay here.

18:28.880 --> 18:31.760
It's too late. Let's make do for tonight.

18:32.160 --> 18:33.360
I'll move back to my parents' tomorrow.

18:35.720 --> 18:36.560
It's okay.

18:38.480 --> 18:42.480
You mean, you're okay with me
not moving back to my parents' place?

18:50.800 --> 18:52.720
I don't want to trouble you.

19:00.440 --> 19:05.680
Actually, I'm very worried
that you'll be staying here.

19:12.640 --> 19:14.120
I won't do anything to you.

19:16.120 --> 19:17.800
I don't mind that,

19:18.440 --> 19:22.120
but you'll find out,
some of my skills aren't perfected yet.

19:24.720 --> 19:25.560
What skills?

19:28.360 --> 19:31.520
Cooking. I can only make noodles.

19:41.920 --> 19:45.120
There are things you're not good at?

19:46.240 --> 19:47.560
I thought you were good at everything.

19:48.760 --> 19:51.320
It's obvious that I have lowered your IQ,

19:51.400 --> 19:52.520
hence the wrong assessment.

19:55.640 --> 19:57.760
Come on, eat. Then do the dishes.

19:58.400 --> 19:59.640
I remember that's your specialty.

20:00.880 --> 20:01.720
Yes, sir.

20:31.560 --> 20:33.040
You can wear these for pajamas.

20:36.160 --> 20:39.120
Go shower. There's a new toothbrush
in the cabinet.

20:39.200 --> 20:40.680
Use my toiletries for now.

21:02.960 --> 21:03.800
They fit you.

21:07.280 --> 21:10.800
I'm going to shower.
Get some sleep. I'll take the couch.

21:10.880 --> 21:12.960
Get another blanket for me
from the closet.

21:15.600 --> 21:18.040
I'll take the couch. I'm shorter.

21:21.480 --> 21:24.840
My couch is too small.
It probably can't fit two people.

21:29.600 --> 21:33.880
Well, you should go shower. Good night.

22:00.200 --> 22:02.360
This is Lord's bed?

22:56.800 --> 23:01.720
Lord's pillow?
Don't tell me, he only has one pillow.

23:44.800 --> 23:45.800
You don't want the pillow?

23:49.400 --> 23:52.560
Your pillow's too thick.
I'm not used to it.

23:54.960 --> 23:57.240
- I'll turn off the lights now.
- Okay.

24:04.520 --> 24:05.760
Let me.

24:08.560 --> 24:10.960
Where's the switch?

25:11.160 --> 25:12.000
Get some rest.

27:10.840 --> 27:11.720
You're up?

27:14.280 --> 27:15.120
Yes.

27:16.480 --> 27:18.800
Go wash up. We're going jogging.

27:20.280 --> 27:21.200
What?

27:21.440 --> 27:23.360
But I don't have any jogging clothes.

27:24.680 --> 27:25.520
I do.

27:46.840 --> 27:48.760
Do you jog every morning?

27:49.120 --> 27:51.400
In school, I go jogging every day,

27:51.480 --> 27:53.200
at the track.

27:54.040 --> 27:55.080
The campus is crowded.

27:55.440 --> 27:57.920
How come I never saw you,
when I went jogging at the track?

27:58.240 --> 27:59.200
I guess I got up earlier than you.

28:05.960 --> 28:06.800
I saw you.

28:19.560 --> 28:22.320
My legs aren't as long as yours. Wait up!

28:28.280 --> 28:30.160
- Professor Li.
- Jogging again?

28:31.160 --> 28:32.120
And this is?

28:32.680 --> 28:34.840
This is my girlfriend, Weiwei.

28:34.920 --> 28:37.280
This is the economics professor, Li Cheng.

28:37.680 --> 28:39.160
- Hi, Professor Li.
- Hello.

28:39.240 --> 28:40.920
- We'll get going now.
- Sure.

28:41.400 --> 28:42.360
Goodbye.

28:47.320 --> 28:48.720
Professor Xiao's son!

28:59.640 --> 29:03.440
Kid! When are you going to
get a girlfriend and get married?

29:03.520 --> 29:05.240
You're nearly 30 now!

29:06.120 --> 29:09.600
Look at Xiao Nai! He's only 22,

29:09.920 --> 29:11.760
and he's brought home a girlfriend.

29:16.960 --> 29:19.920
- Breakfast at home or dine out?
- Dine out!

29:21.080 --> 29:22.800
I mean,

29:22.880 --> 29:26.160
there's a huge discrepancy
between your looks and your noodles.

29:26.320 --> 29:27.160
They taste so-so.

29:27.720 --> 29:30.720
- You're complaining about me already?
- No way!

29:31.040 --> 29:34.080
I'm just being honest.
I know a good place. I'll take you.

29:35.200 --> 29:38.360
Come on, let's go.

29:44.520 --> 29:47.400
Nai, you're finally back!

29:47.480 --> 29:49.880
K.O. has been harassing me nonstop.

29:50.280 --> 29:51.480
Harassing you? How?

29:52.880 --> 29:55.040
Mr. Mei, how is he harassing you?

29:55.120 --> 29:58.120
Tell us everything.
Don't leave out any detail.

29:58.240 --> 30:00.000
We'll get justice for you.

30:00.400 --> 30:03.240
He wants me to team up with him
in that old game.

30:04.360 --> 30:07.240
- How can he do that? That's too much!
- Right?

30:07.680 --> 30:10.080
He said, he was mocked.

30:10.160 --> 30:11.120
He wants to even the score.

30:12.040 --> 30:14.280
Players come and go in the gaming world.

30:14.640 --> 30:16.040
What's the point in evening the score?

30:17.600 --> 30:19.640
K.O. is right.

30:20.040 --> 30:22.320
You toyed with his feelings, Mr. Hao.

30:23.080 --> 30:24.400
You must do right by him.

30:25.560 --> 30:27.720
Nai, help me out here.

30:29.680 --> 30:32.560
This is good. I was worried

30:32.880 --> 30:35.880
K.O. wouldn't stay after a year.
Now my problem's solved.

30:38.640 --> 30:42.920
You're so heartless, Nai.
You're using me for a political marriage?

30:44.280 --> 30:45.120
I'll give you a bonus.

30:47.880 --> 30:48.920
I'd only sell out for a grand.

30:58.760 --> 30:59.600
Yes!

31:04.640 --> 31:06.120
Make way...

31:06.200 --> 31:09.680
K.O., let's go team up later.
Dinner's my treat.

31:09.840 --> 31:12.920
Mei, your sense of virtue is so flimsy.

31:13.000 --> 31:14.040
Get back to work.

31:15.320 --> 31:16.680
There are few men nowadays

31:16.760 --> 31:19.760
who are as virtuous as me.

31:19.840 --> 31:22.480
I think Mr. Xiao's offer was too high.

31:22.560 --> 31:24.240
How is Mei worth a grand?

31:24.320 --> 31:26.840
I'd ask for 50 percent off, plus a gift.

31:27.480 --> 31:30.440
If K.O. successfully gets Hao Mei,

31:30.520 --> 31:33.480
we'll have to call him Girly Mei.

31:33.840 --> 31:36.360
Girly Mei, I want dinner, too.

31:36.440 --> 31:38.040
At least some wedding candy?

31:38.720 --> 31:39.720
Get lost...

31:41.200 --> 31:42.160
Let's meet in a bit, programming division.

31:44.360 --> 31:46.360
Okay...

31:50.920 --> 31:52.040
Ms. Weiwei?

31:55.120 --> 31:56.160
What?

31:56.880 --> 31:59.000
You're wearing the same skirt
from yesterday.

32:01.360 --> 32:04.080
Is it because last night...

32:06.880 --> 32:10.280
Yugong, it's only because...

32:13.880 --> 32:14.720
I'm poor.

32:32.920 --> 32:35.200
What do you think, programming master?

32:35.520 --> 32:38.440
Is the motion smoother now?

32:38.520 --> 32:41.200
Have those freakish eyes of yours
noticed other problems?

32:43.080 --> 32:46.600
There is no end to optimization.
Men should always strive for more.

32:47.160 --> 32:48.280
You sure you want me
to point out problems?

32:50.080 --> 32:53.200
I beg of you, forget what I just said.

32:54.360 --> 32:57.640
When we were rushed for time
and prioritized progress,

32:58.040 --> 33:01.560
a reloading window would pop up
during scene switches.

33:01.640 --> 33:03.560
We have now fixed the bug.

33:04.160 --> 33:07.280
Good. Let's try
the Hebo flood-fighting quest again,

33:07.480 --> 33:08.760
and simulate multiple players
at the rescue.

33:22.960 --> 33:25.720
The transition time
has increased by 30 percent.

33:26.120 --> 33:27.520
The textures the art division made

33:27.600 --> 33:30.200
were distorted
and the resolution was lower in the game.

33:30.560 --> 33:31.720
After optimization,

33:32.080 --> 33:34.040
our engine has perfectly achieved
the expected result.

33:38.560 --> 33:40.800
But when I go into
the Hebo flood-fighting quest,

33:40.880 --> 33:42.160
it takes up 900 MB bytes of my RAM.

33:43.720 --> 33:46.560
That's normal. Hebo flood-fighting quest

33:46.640 --> 33:49.200
is one of the most complex scenes
in our demo.

33:49.280 --> 33:51.360
There are millions of polygon faces alone.

33:51.640 --> 33:53.400
The textures are also very complex.

33:53.560 --> 33:55.880
Then we're back to the same old question.

33:56.480 --> 33:59.200
It might require players
to have high-end equipment.

34:00.000 --> 34:02.840
Nai, haven't you been working
on optimization?

34:02.920 --> 34:03.760
How's that going?

34:04.600 --> 34:05.800
The main problem

34:06.080 --> 34:08.639
is the same,
the textures take up too much RAM.

34:09.280 --> 34:10.960
The models are too complex.

34:11.159 --> 34:12.760
But in order to simulate
global illumination,

34:13.080 --> 34:15.280
we can only use a huge amount of RAM
to cut down on time.

34:15.880 --> 34:18.600
I plan to finish the tool
on September 15.

34:19.000 --> 34:21.840
Then I'll use the tool
to automatically simplify models

34:22.040 --> 34:23.400
and decrease textures.

34:26.600 --> 34:28.159
Aside from my work here,

34:28.520 --> 34:30.199
we have pretty much solved

34:30.480 --> 34:31.679
all problems from the first alpha test.

34:32.239 --> 34:34.560
The final demo is still a month away.

34:34.840 --> 34:35.880
We have plenty of time.

34:36.480 --> 34:41.199
From now on, you don't have to work
on weekends anymore.

34:45.520 --> 34:47.360
But when we were in a rush,

34:48.000 --> 34:50.400
some of our coding wasn't so textbook

34:50.840 --> 34:52.159
and had poor scalability.

34:53.679 --> 34:56.840
We have plenty of time now.
You can reconfigure some more.

35:01.400 --> 35:02.240
Meeting adjourned.

35:12.560 --> 35:13.760
I'm telling you,

35:13.840 --> 35:15.920
Hanyan said he searched BIT high and low,

35:16.000 --> 35:18.280
but he didn't find Luwei Weiwei anywhere.

35:19.480 --> 35:21.800
I knew it! With her looks,

35:21.880 --> 35:24.960
how low-key can she be?
Someone has to have seen her.

35:25.160 --> 35:28.120
I was right, wasn't I?
She's pretending to be a college student.

35:28.320 --> 35:31.320
I can spot the harlot in her,
in an instant.

35:32.760 --> 35:34.440
So, she lied to us?

35:35.040 --> 35:37.240
Why would Luwei Weiwei bother?

35:37.320 --> 35:38.600
Even if she hasn't gone to college,

35:39.000 --> 35:40.560
we wouldn't belittle her. Right?

35:40.920 --> 35:44.240
Don't you get it? Her real identity
must be too embarrassing.

35:47.880 --> 35:49.680
Zhenshui, don't drink alone.

35:50.080 --> 35:52.240
You and Yaoyao should drink a toast.

35:52.600 --> 35:55.600
You dumped the wrong one,
so you can meet the right one.

35:57.240 --> 35:58.880
We're from different worlds.

35:59.240 --> 36:00.760
Why do you always compare her to me?

36:09.120 --> 36:11.480
What's wrong, Shaoxiang?

36:14.000 --> 36:14.840
Check, please!

36:21.520 --> 36:23.160
Just a moment.

36:25.360 --> 36:28.160
Can't you see Yaoyao is still eating,
Zhenshui?

36:29.600 --> 36:32.080
I'm settling the bill.
You can keep eating.

36:32.920 --> 36:34.960
This is the last time I'm treating you.

36:35.720 --> 36:36.560
Have fun.

36:40.160 --> 36:42.240
What are you saying, Shaoxiang?

36:49.720 --> 36:50.560
Okay. Thanks.

36:53.920 --> 36:55.640
Think of this as a breakup meal.

36:57.160 --> 36:59.360
We should break up, Yaoyao.

37:00.960 --> 37:01.840
What?

37:05.960 --> 37:08.040
Wait! Why? Why are we breaking up?

37:08.120 --> 37:09.800
Weren't we okay yesterday?

37:10.320 --> 37:12.000
Is it because of that wench, Luwei Weiwei?

37:12.080 --> 37:14.440
I knew it! With her looks,

37:14.520 --> 37:15.640
she's bound to steal boyfriends.

37:15.840 --> 37:16.680
Enough!

37:18.640 --> 37:19.560
Aren't you bored,

37:20.040 --> 37:22.680
talking trash
behind other people's backs all the time?

37:23.400 --> 37:26.760
Even if you're not bored, I am.
Let's just end it here.

37:28.360 --> 37:30.280
What's the meaning of this?
Explain yourself!

37:34.400 --> 37:36.440
- Shaoxiang!
- Yaoyao!

37:36.760 --> 37:40.120
It's all your fault!
You're always trashing others.

37:40.360 --> 37:41.600
Now you've upset Zhenshui.

37:42.520 --> 37:45.200
Stupid Zhenshui! He'll regret this.

37:46.480 --> 37:50.560
Don't be sad, Yaoyao.
There are plenty of fish in the sea.

37:50.640 --> 37:52.960
You're so pretty, you'll find
a tall, rich, and handsome guy.

37:55.240 --> 37:59.280
But aren't golden bachelors like Zhenshui
few and far between?

38:28.160 --> 38:29.000
Mr. Zhen?

38:30.360 --> 38:32.800
Get me that intern,
Zhao Erxi's address.

38:33.240 --> 38:35.360
But we didn't ask interns
to provide their addresses.

38:35.960 --> 38:38.480
Find a way to get it. I want to know ASAP.

38:39.520 --> 38:42.680
By the way, don't let her know,
you're doing this for me.

38:43.840 --> 38:44.800
I see.

39:05.160 --> 39:07.360
Erxi, fill out this form.

39:08.720 --> 39:09.920
What's this?

39:10.000 --> 39:12.000
At the end of the internship,

39:12.080 --> 39:15.320
we always mail interns
a commemorative book.

39:15.960 --> 39:18.640
Why mail it? Why don't we just pick it up?

39:20.040 --> 39:21.240
Hold on.

39:26.280 --> 39:27.360
Thanks.

39:28.040 --> 39:30.160
I'll ask others to fill it out.

40:03.120 --> 40:06.280
Baogui Garden? It's on my way.

40:16.280 --> 40:18.440
- It's all good.
- I'll get on it.

40:28.720 --> 40:31.680
Hello, Xiaoling?
Let me find a quieter place.

40:38.720 --> 40:40.360
Hello, Xiaoling? Go ahead.

40:40.840 --> 40:42.240
What's going on with you and Erxi?

40:42.880 --> 40:45.800
Sisi told me,
when she spoke to Erxi yesterday,

40:45.880 --> 40:47.400
Erxi sounded weird.

40:47.480 --> 40:48.960
She asked Erxi to hand you the phone,

40:49.440 --> 40:51.520
then Erxi stuttered for a while,

40:51.760 --> 40:53.720
before she said, you'd moved out.

40:54.040 --> 40:56.080
Why did she say you'd moved out?

40:56.720 --> 40:59.880
Are you living with Lord? Already? No way!

41:01.080 --> 41:02.960
I don't know what to say.

41:03.560 --> 41:05.360
Erxi and I both need to calm down.

41:07.640 --> 41:12.600
Don't scare me. Is it... that serious?

41:13.960 --> 41:15.600
You're always the rational one, Weiwei.

41:15.680 --> 41:16.960
You know how Erxi is.

41:17.040 --> 41:18.320
She's silly and nutty.

41:18.880 --> 41:20.520
You should be the bigger person.

41:22.360 --> 41:26.440
But sometimes,
I feel a little indignant, too.

41:26.800 --> 41:29.360
What? You feel a little what?

41:30.600 --> 41:32.320
It's nothing.
Let's talk when school starts.

41:33.640 --> 41:36.400
Fine, don't have a falling out for real.

41:36.480 --> 41:38.800
It'll make me think
my place has bad feng shui.

41:41.920 --> 41:44.200
Your place has great feng shui.

41:44.720 --> 41:47.400
There are always cute guys
in the swimming pool.

41:48.760 --> 41:49.840
I took a look.

41:49.920 --> 41:51.920
The window looks out to the garden.

41:52.000 --> 41:55.080
There's a swimming pool,
and a cute guy is swimming.

41:57.400 --> 42:00.920
Hello, Weiwei? What's wrong, Weiwei?

42:01.640 --> 42:04.880
Nothing. I have to go.

42:08.040 --> 42:08.880
Hello?

44:51.600 --> 44:54.040
Subtitle translation by Lu Yuhan
